{"tid":2283642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[去年今日] 嘉里物流中心黑衣青年墮樓亡 事後陶輝親自帶隊到現場一帶","createTime":"2020-11-12T17:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T01:09:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5aff61e72ee578987c88f120c91e9cebfd58f5f9","tid":2283642,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/719738615176776\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F719738615176776&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BytOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=445a0faa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/719738615176776</a><br />\n<br />\n【0232 荃灣】黑衣青年墮樓亡    陶輝帶隊到場<br />\n周三（13日）晚上，一名黑衣黑褲青年倒臥在葵涌勝耀街嘉里物流中心對出位置，地面有大片血跡，他被送院後證實死亡。有目擊者稱他是從高處墮下。<br />\n凌晨，署理新界南總區指揮官陶輝帶同防暴及速龍警員，到嘉里物流中心一帶視察。陶輝視察後離去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2615133451905592\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2615133451905592&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2BytOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=def85909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2615133451905592</a>"},{"pid":"7779c50d8182260f57ae13e961c70b42ce14b5b8","tid":2283642,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5adccaef832a7f78f634c09cda868839e77f9c2c","tid":2283642,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T17:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},